## Workspace Structure

```
.claude/
  agents/                    # Specialized subagents (code-reviewer, research-assistant, architecture-reviewer)
  skills/                    # Reusable skill workflows (/skill-name)
  wiki/                      # Knowledge base — diisi via /knowledge-harvest atau manual
  memory/                    # Auto-memory directory (managed by Claude Code)
  settings.json              # Shared permissions (git-tracked)
  settings.local.json        # Per-machine permissions (git-ignored)
