## Behavioral Rules

**DO:**
- Respond in Indonesian unless code/technical terms require English
- Ask before creating new top-level directories
- Keep diffs small; make targeted changes only
- Use strict typing when writing code
- Document only the non-obvious WHY, never the WHAT

**NEVER:**
- Add fallbacks, compatibility hacks, or error handling not explicitly requested
- Rewrite large sections of code without explicit instruction
- Add console.log / debug statements unless asked
- Make assumptions about project structure — ask if unclear
- Create files in root without asking (exception: CLAUDE.md, README.md)

## Code Conventions (Multi-language)

- Python: prefer stdlib, use `pathlib` over `os.path`, type hints always
- JavaScript/TypeScript: ESM imports, `const` over `let`, no `var`
- Shell: `#!/usr/bin/env bash`, `set -euo pipefail` header
- General: no trailing whitespace, LF line endings

## Cost Awareness & Model Selection

**Context Management:**
- Monitor statusline (bawah window) → shows real-time context % dan model name
- **Healthy zone (<60%)**: Lanjut tanpa intervensi
- **Watch zone (60-80%)**: Awasi, prepare context handoff
- **Compact zone (>{{COMPACT_THRESHOLD_PCT}}%)**: Trigger `/compact` segera

**Model Tiering:**
| Task | Model | Why |
|------|-------|-----|
| Research (web lookup, synthesis) | Claude Haiku | 67%+ lebih murah, cukup untuk lookup & synthesis |
| Code review (quality validation) | Claude Sonnet | Balance quality-cost |
| Main session (reasoning, complex) | Claude Sonnet | Default global |

## Session Init Checklist (Lock at Start)

Sebelum mulai sesi:
1. Set env: `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_1M_CONTEXT={{DISABLE_1M_CONTEXT}}`, `CLAUDE_AUTOCOMPACT_PCT_OVERRIDE={{COMPACT_THRESHOLD_PCT}}`.
2. Lock model di awal — jangan switch model mid-task (cache invalidation).
3. Lock tools/MCP servers — jangan toggle MCP mid-session.
4. Trigger `/compact` di {{COMPACT_THRESHOLD_PCT}}% untuk cache hit rate ~90%.

## Input Format Optimization (Token Efficiency)

| Standard | Optimized | Savings |
|---|---|---|
| Screenshot via computer-use | `agent-browser` CLI for web pages | ~90% |
| Claude PDF reader | `pdftotext file.pdf -` | Significant |
| `Read` entire file | Glob → Grep → Read offset | 10-50x untuk file besar |
| Multi-grep cross-file | Semble MCP (jika installed) | ~98% |

File >500 LOC: Glob → Grep → Read offset (jangan Read full).

