## Troubleshooting Quick-Guide

**Problem: "MCP server github won't start"**
- Check: Is GITHUB_TOKEN set? → [.env.example](.env.example)
- Fix: Create .env from .env.example, fill GITHUB_TOKEN, reload terminal

**Problem: "Permission denied on git command"**
- Check: Does .claude/settings.local.json have "Bash(git *)" in allow list?

**When in doubt:**
- Check [.claude/AGENTS.md](.claude/AGENTS.md) for agent questions
- Check [.claude/SKILLS.md](.claude/SKILLS.md) for skill questions
- See [.claude/SETTINGS.md](.claude/SETTINGS.md) for permission issues
